sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    actor U as Seeker (User)
    participant V as View (HTML/DOM)
    participant P as Presenter (JavaScript)
    participant A as API Endpoint (search.php)
    participant M as Model (AdsLogic.php)
    participant DB as MySQL Database

    Note over U, V: User Interaction
    U->>V: Insert Filters (City, Price)
    U->>V: Click "Search"
    
    V->>P: 'submit' event (preventDefault)
    activate P
    Note right of V: The Presenter intercepts the event<br/>and blocks page reload
    
    P->>P: Client-side Input Validation
    
    %% PRESENTER -> API (AJAX CALL)
    Note over P, A: HTTP / JSON Communication
    P->>A: FETCH GET /api/search?city=Parma
    activate A
    
    %% API -> MODEL
    A->>M: getCompatibleAds(userId, city)
    activate M
    
    %% MODEL -> DB
    M->>DB: SELECT * FROM ads WHERE city = ?
    activate DB
    DB-->>M: Return ResultSet (Raw Ads)
    deactivate DB
    
    M->>DB: SELECT preferences FROM users WHERE id = ?
    activate DB
    DB-->>M: Return User Preferences
    deactivate DB

    %% BUSINESS LOGIC (MATCHING)
    loop For each Ad
        M->>M: Calculate Compatibility Score<br/>(Proprietary Algorithm)
    end
    
    %% DATA RETURN
    M-->>A: Return Array (Ads + Score)
    deactivate M
    
    A-->>P: Return JSON Response
    deactivate A

    %% PRESENTER -> VIEW (DOM UPDATE)
    alt Results found
        P->>V: Generate HTML Cards (Loop)
        V-->>U: Show list ordered by Score
    else No results
        P->>V: Show "No ads found" Message
        V-->>U: Show error message
    end
    
    deactivate P
